name: CoreAPI Tools_Database_TableDefinition
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Tools-Database Definition
about:
Description

Planet 9-API Tools_Database_TableDefinition enables you to create and maintain Planet 9 Tables definitions.

API Tools_Database_TableDefinition is the API to access Planet 9 tables definitions and to perform the certain operations performed on table definitions..

Every app must have the right roles( permissions) that enables to access the planet 9 Tools_Database_TableDefinition of your system.

Operations Performed

Get

Get the definition of selected table

RequestID
ResponseGet(object)- Definition                          

List

Get the list of tables definition. 

ResponseList(array)- Definition           

Delete

Delete the Background Job

RequestDelete(object)- Definition

Save

Save or create the new job

RequestSave(object)-Definition
